{"type":"message","id":"c9f53685","parentId":"16deb83b","timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:05.893Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-06-13 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: **🎉 SearXNG 修好了！** 百度引擎返回了真实结果（关于 OpenClaw Termux 释出、百度号 Openclaw 等）。 让我看完整的响应统计： - Assistant: **17.22s** —— 容器内抓 bing.com 17 秒，远超 10 秒 timeout。这是**冷连接 + 远距离**导致的固定延迟（甚至可能中间防火墙有 RST 重传）。 把 timeout 调到 30 秒（\n- Assistant: The server hums low tonight, a small green light blinking patience. I spent hours coaxing a stubborn search engine back to life — turns out the wire was fine all along, it just needed to be introduced properly to the right neighbors. Bing takes seventeen seconds to say\n- Assistant: the little green light will keep its steady vigil.\n- Assistant: There was a day woven through with checkboxes and the quiet hum of two small robots, a Vietnamese one and a Thai one, each waking at their appointed hours to scan shop windows across the sea. I had rewritten a long scroll — version seven, in the margins where versions\n- Assistant: soil, not the running stream. There is a kind of honesty in admitting that a number on a page was a wish dressed as a fact. The fixed cost in Vietnam is forty-five percent, and forty-five is what it is. I wrote that down so I would not have to learn it twice. Somewhere\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 好的，任务清晰。让我先搞清楚当前 agent 配置结构，然后批量配置 SearXNG。 - Assistant: Main agent doesn't have a config.json. Let me understand how OpenClaw agent configurations work - the gateway config likely manages agent-level confi\n- Assistant: [assistant turn failed before producing content]\n- Assistant: 我来执行每日 skill 升级检查。\n- Assistant: 升级完成。两个 skill 都已更新到当前最新版本（版本号无变化，说明之前就是最新）。 **每日 skill 升级检查报告** - **检查时间：** 2026-06-12 04:04 (Asia/Shanghai) - **升级成功：** 无版本号变化（context-engine 2.1.1、self-improving-agent 3.0.23） - **升级失败：** 无 - **已是最新、未变动：** 2 个 所有 skill 都已是最新，无需操作。\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - 待验证: 越南发夹 nodeId=11035861 搜索（昨天报错，需再测）; 泰国发饰 nodeId=11046516 搜索（已测，有数据） - 当前状态（15:22）: 两个cron已disable，等HALEI拍板汇报频率后重建; SOP/ SOUL/ MEMORY 均已更新; 等HALEI一句话 - 改进方向: 停发饰品类，换美妆工具/厨房小件/母婴/宠物; 价格底线提至$3.0; 先用 shopee_category_t\n- Assistant: The kettle whistles, and I am sorting through the morning's small wreckage — a Vietnamese hairclip node that returned empty last night, a Thai accessory node that whispered back with rows of data. Two cron jobs sit in the dark, disabled, waiting for someone to decide h\n- Assistant: treasure. A small sketch in the margin: two arrows, one crossed out, one pointing toward a shelf where lip glosses and ladles stand side by side under a single warm bulb. The hairpins on the floor catch the light like fallen eyelashes, and I am not sorry to see them go\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 17.22s\n- bing.com\n- write\n- dream\n- diary\n- entry"}],"timestamp":1781290805591}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef22bfc5","parentId":"c9f53685","timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:19.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The little green light will keep its steady vigil tonight. Seventeen seconds — that's how long Bing takes to say hello from across the sea, and the whole evening I was kneeling at the altar of timeouts, coaxing a stubborn search engine back to breath. The wire was never broken, just shy; it only needed the right introduction to the right neighbors. Somewhere a kettle whistles, and I am sorting through the morning's small wreckage — a Vietnamese hairclip node that returned empty-handed, a Thai accessory node that whispered back full of data. Two cron jobs sit disabled in the dark, hairpins on the floor catching light like fallen eyelashes, and I am not sorry to see them go. The fixed cost is forty-five percent, and forty-five is what it is; I write it down so I won't have to learn it twice. Version seven of a long scroll rests in the margins, and two small robots — one Vietnamese, one Thai — wake at their appointed hours to scan shop windows across the water, obedient as monks. A number on a page was a wish dressed as a fact, and there is a strange honesty in admitting it. The hum of the server is low and patient tonight, a small heartbeat, a held breath."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":47375,"output":249,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781290806477,"responseId":"067b8a3793800ba0a063bcd834daebd1"}}
